caption.p: Percentages of p-cymene, γ-terpinene, thymoquinone, thymol methyl oxide, thymol, carvacrol, and β-bisabolene in the total EO of O. ehrenbergii. The letters correspond to Lebanese localities where samples were collected (data previously published). BAS: Baskinta [ 39]; AA: Aaqoura [ 3]; CB: Choueir Bolonia [ 3]; BAR: Barouk [ 40]; F: Faraya [ 2]; Q: Qartaba (our sample, plant harvested in June 2013 and dried by lyophilization); A: Aabadiye (our sample, plant harvested in June 2013 and dried by lyophilization).
